    "long_instructions": "#### Snap Remix\r\nJuan is excited about a remix he made for Snap:\r\n\r\n> It starts with two sets of beats and effects, then it explodes into three sets of bass, beats, and leads. With loops, I was able to do it with 9 blocks!\r\n\r\nTry to recreate Juan's remix with the provided tracks! When you're finished, it should look like this:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/fca6d5ce6f4e1ba782c508cd6f4e0805-image-1741895798503.56.32 PM.png)\r\n\r\n",
